node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Coach Legend on July 30, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'A HIGH-INCOME SKILL GIVES YOU THE FINANCIAL CONFIDENCE TO MAKE MONEY ANYTIME, ANYWHERE. C COACH LEGEND'.

node.text:
Most people tell you to get a safe job.

That having a safe job is the best way to have job security.

Well, let me ask you.

Do you think you could easily be replaced in your job?

If you quit, wouldn't someone fill your spot in a few weeks?

If you're that replaceable, do you think there is really such thing as "job security?"

Exactly.

So don't rely on your job to give you a good income.

Rely on your skills.

Develop a high-income skill that can make you more than $10K a month.

And rely on YOURSELF to make you money.

Not anyone else.

Comment below if this makes sense.

If you are ready to develop your high-income skills, DM me.

I see people everywhere wanting to change the world and that’s cool. 

But why not start by helping one person first. 

Because helping one person will change that person's world in ways you couldn't imagine. 

Share with me in the comments a time you helped a stranger.

node.text:
If you make $400-600 a week in an online business, they’ll say their job pays the same. 

If you make $1,000 a week they’ll say you have to pay taxes at the end… 

If you make $100,000+ a year they’ll say you’re scamming people…

If you buy a new car, they’ll say you leased it… 

If you get on a commercial flight they’ll say it’s not a private jet 🛩 

If you get on a private jet they’ll say it’s not a G6… 

People will hate on every move you make if you don’t fit in their mold. I’ve noticed that most of the people that hate on me cannot do what I do. They can’t build a massive business, mentor an organization, they can’t motivate through a computer screen, they’ll accuse you of lack of leadership and skill, but wouldn’t dare compare currencies… This is the world we live in, it’s called the Land of Haters and to that I say, ENJOY THE SHOW. Cheers 🥂

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Coach Legend in SALES. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'THE 3 MOST IMPORTANT SKILLS IN SALES 1.UNDERSTAND YOUR CUSTOMERS 2.DISCOVER YOUR CUSTOMER'S PAIN POINTS 3.HANDLE OBJECTIONS C COACH LEGEND'.

node.text:
Before you close your prospects into your product or service, you must understand them.⁣
⁣
Why are they seeking a solution to their problem?⁣
⁣
What are their pain points?⁣
⁣
Why is change an absolute necessity for them now?⁣
⁣
Once you have this figured out, they will give you objections about why they shouldn’t move forwards today.⁣
⁣
Their brain will throw up resistance, even if they really want change.⁣
⁣
Your ability to overcome these objections with finesse will help you win the sale.⁣
⁣
What do you find the most challenging about the sales process?⁣
⁣
Comment below.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Coach Legend on July 26, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'SOMETIMES IT CAN TAKE 10 YEARS TO GET TO THAT1 YEAR THAT CHANGES YOUR LIFE. C COACH LEGEND'.

node.text:
Just because you start your journey to success doesn’t mean you’ll see results in the first year. 

Sure, some people do… 

But for the majority of people, it can take many years before they reach the year that changes their life. 

In my first 5 years in business, I didn't take a single day off. 

I worked countless hours every day. 

And by the end of that 5 years, I had so many  businesses and accrued a lot of debt. 

I was on the razor’s edge of failure when I finally got to the year that changed my life. 

So, no matter where you are on your journey. 

If you haven’t reached the life-changing year yet, keep going. 

It could be just around the corner. 

Tag someone who should see this.
